    "source": {
      "book": "Materia"
    },
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You manifest a ravine of gravitational energy in a line originating from you that is 100 feet long and 5 feet wide. Each creature in that line must make a Constitution saving throw, taking [[/r 10d10]] force damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>Each creature within 10 feet of the line but not in it must succeed on a Strength saving throw or take [[/r 10d10]] force damage and be pulled toward the line until the creature is in its area.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels. </strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 2d10]] for each slot level above 6th.</p><",
